{"word":"H3477 - יָשָׁר - yâshâr - yaw-shawr' - Convenient","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָשָׁר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>yâshâr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>yaw-shawr'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Convenient"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"செவ்வைபான, மனஉற்சாகமுள்ள, உத்தமர், நிமிர்ந்த, யாசேர், செம்மையான, நீதிமான், சரியான, உத்தமன், நலமான, சன்மார்க்கன், யதார்த்தமான, நீதியுள்ள, நியாயமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"straight, upright, correct, right"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H3474 - יָשַׁר - yâshar - yaw-shar'/3474\">H3474</a>; <i>straight</i> (literally or figuratively): - convenient, equity, Jasher, just, meet (-est), + pleased well right (-eous), straight, (most) upright (-ly, -ness)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3474 - יָשַׁר - yâshar - yaw-shar'/3474\">H3474</a>, <a href=\"#/H3475 - יֵשֶׁר - Yêsher - yay'-sher/3475\">H3475</a>, <a href=\"#/H3476 - יֹשֶׁר - yôsher - yo'-sher/3476\">H3476</a>, <a href=\"#/H3477 - יָשָׁר - yâshâr - yaw-shawr'/3477\">H3477</a>, <a href=\"#/H3483 - יִשְׁרָה - yishrâh - yish-raw'/3483\">H3483</a>, <a href=\"#/H3484 - יְשֻׁרוּן - Yᵉshurûwn - yesh-oo-roon'/3484\">H3484</a>, <a href=\"#/H4334 - מִישֹׁור - mîyshôwr - mee-shore'/4334\">H4334</a>, <a href=\"#/H4339 - מֵישָׁר - mêyshâr - may-shawr'/4339\">H4339</a>, <a href=\"#/H8289 - שָׁרֹון - Shârôwn - shaw-rone'/8289\">H8289</a>, <a href=\"#/H8290 - שָׁרֹונִי - Shârôwnîy - shaw-ro-nee'/8290\">H8290</a>"}]}